'''糖果屋公司''' ({{lang-en|'''CANDY HOUSE, Inc.'''}}) 是由兩位{{link|史丹佛大學}}學生[[古哲明|古哲明]]、[[신종호|신종호]](申宗浩)<ref>{{cite web|title=HANDS ON: SESAME SMART LOCK|url=http://www.digitaltrends.com/home/sesame-smart-lock-hands-on|publisher=Digital Trends|date=April 27, 2015|accessdate=2017-02-05|archive-date=2017-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170206105731/http://www.digitaltrends.com/home/sesame-smart-lock-hands-on/|dead-url=no}}</ref>於2014年6月3日在宿舍裡創立。糖果屋公司是一家美國跨國公司，總部位於[[美国|美国]][[加利福尼亚|加利福尼亚]][[帕羅奧圖|帕羅奧圖]]，致力於設計、研發和銷售[[創新型智慧機械|創新型智慧機械]]、[[行動應用程式|行動應用程式]]、[[線上服務|線上服務]]和[[消費電子|消費電子]]。糖果屋的第一個產品 [[Sesame_US1|Sesame US1]] 於2010年代中期助長了[[智慧家庭|智慧家庭]]革命。<ref>{{cite web|title=Sesame's smart door lock lets you in with a simple knock|url=https://www.engadget.com/2015/02/25/sesame-smart-door-lock|publisher=Engadget|date=February 25, 2015|accessdate=2017-02-05|archive-date=2017-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170206103611/https://www.engadget.com/2015/02/25/sesame-smart-door-lock/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Sesame is one of the cheapest smart locks you can buy|url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/4/3/8337683/sesame-smart-lock-kickstarter-cheap-hands-on|publisher=The Verge|date=April 3, 2015|accessdate=2017-02-05|archive-date=2017-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170206022027/http://www.theverge.com/2015/4/3/8337683/sesame-smart-lock-kickstarter-cheap-hands-on|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Sesame kickstarts some new competition for August|url=https://www.cnet.com/products/sesame-smart-lock/preview|publisher=CNET|date=February 25, 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170206021924/https://www.cnet.com/products/sesame-smart-lock/preview/|archivedate=2017年2月6日|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Open Sesame: Gadget Turns Lock Into Smart Lock in Seconds|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/tech/gadgets/open-sesame-gadget-turns-lock-smart-lock-seconds-n312886|publisher=NBC NEWS|date=February 25, 2015|accessdate=2017-02-05|archive-date=2017-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170205191307/http://www.nbcnews.com/tech/gadgets/open-sesame-gadget-turns-lock-smart-lock-seconds-n312886|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=New 'smart lock' lets user ditch keys - and open their door with a knock|url=https://uk.news.yahoo.com/new--smart-lock--lets-user-ditch-keys---and-open-their-door-with-a-knock-145407440.html|publisher=YAHOO NEWS|date=February 27, 2015|accessdate=2017-02-05|archive-date=2017-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170205183613/https://uk.news.yahoo.com/new--smart-lock--lets-user-ditch-keys---and-open-their-door-with-a-knock-145407440.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

